    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Elementalist is a challenging movement puzzle platformer, where you collect elemental orbs that give you powers, such as double jump, horizontal dash, ground slam, and teleporting shot. After you collect an ability, it will be the next one you use, so be careful about the order of your actions. Some puzzles will require you to think outside the box.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Demo features:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 distinct areas </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >41 unique puzzle rooms </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 difficult bonus puzzles </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect movement abilities in an Elemental Stack.</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111100/extras/c889118d685698399df7d109fd3b2fa8.poster.avif?t=1767478951\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111100/extras/c889118d685698399df7d109fd3b2fa8.webm?t=1767478951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111100/extras/c889118d685698399df7d109fd3b2fa8.mp4?t=1767478951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use the most recently collected ability with just one button.</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111100/extras/553621dad0e7ecd9c53bd858dfc2eef1.poster.avif?t=1767478951\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111100/extras/553621dad0e7ecd9c53bd858dfc2eef1.webm?t=1767478951\" type=